# Response headers applied to all served paths by Cloudflare Workers Static
# Assets. This file is shipped as part of the build's `dist/` output and
# Cloudflare reads it to attach headers per matching path. Format docs:
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/headers/
#
# Notes per directive:
#
# Content-Security-Policy:
#   - default-src 'self'                      everything not otherwise specified must be same-origin
#   - script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' blob:
#                                             no inline scripts; 'wasm-unsafe-eval' allows
#                                             WebAssembly.instantiate for the Sleeve WASM.
#                                             blob: is REQUIRED by xxdk-wasm's worker bootstrap:
#                                             it fetches wasm_exec.js, wraps it in a blob URL, and
#                                             boots its worker from a blob script that importScripts
#                                             that blob URL — all governed by script-src(-elem).
#                                             Verified empirically 2026-07-17: removing blob: blocks
#                                             go-online with a CSP violation (AUDIT-2026-07-001;
#                                             trade-off recorded in ADR-0014 amendment). Revisit if
#                                             xxdk-wasm ever ships a same-origin worker entry file.
#   - style-src                               allow inline styles (Tailwind utility classes mixed with JSX `style={}`)
#                                             and Google Fonts CSS
#   - font-src                                Google Fonts files (Roboto + JetBrains Mono)
#   - img-src                                 own + data: (SVG inlining, blob: for QR canvases)
#   - connect-src                             same-origin + indexer + cMix infra (gateways *.xxnode.io,
#                                             registration/scheduling *.cmix.rip — gRPC-web over HTTPS) +
#                                             localhost dev RPC + wss://*
#                                             The wss://* wildcard is intentional — users can configure custom
#                                             RPC URLs, so the set of hosts can't be enumerated in a static
#                                             header. It subsumes the chain RPC hosts (xx.network/dwellir).
#   - worker-src                              service worker is same-origin only
#   - manifest-src                            PWA manifest same-origin
#   - frame-ancestors 'none'                  prevent click-jacking via iframe embedding on attacker pages
#   - base-uri 'self'                         disallow attacker-controlled <base> tag injection
#   - form-action 'self'                      no form submissions can leave this origin
#   - object-src 'none'                       no Flash/legacy embeds at all
#
# Strict-Transport-Security:
#   2-year HSTS with subdomain coverage. The `preload` token is intentionally
#   omitted: submitting xx.network to the browser preload list would force HTTPS
#   on every *.xx.network subdomain, browser-side and hard to undo. Do NOT add
#   `preload` until every *.xx.network subdomain is confirmed HTTPS-ready.
#   includeSubDomains is kept (header-scoped, reversible).
#
# Permissions-Policy:
#   Camera allowed for the QR scanner. USB and HID allowed (same-origin
#   only) for Ledger hardware-wallet connections — WebHID carries desktop,
#   WebUSB carries Android over a USB-C cable; both still require an
#   explicit per-device user grant via the browser's chooser, so allowing
#   the feature does not expose devices without user action. Everything
#   else explicitly denied so a compromised dependency can't quietly
#   start the mic or read geolocation.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data: blob:; connect-src 'self' https://indexer.xx.network https://*.xxnode.io:* https://*.cmix.rip:* ws://localhost:* wss://*; worker-src 'self' blob:; manifest-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; object-src 'none'
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(self), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=(), usb=(self), hid=(self), accelerometer=(), gyroscope=()
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
